name: Alliance Tournament Cup
description:
Passed on to the winners after every tournament, the magnificent Alliance Tournament cup is perhaps the most coveted prize in New Eden. Glory and fame await the holders, who had to defeat the competition posed by the elite combat teams of their opponents in the one of the most gruelling, bloody and exciting tournaments in existence.
